Day 22: Visualize Workflows!
📊 "A visible workflow is a productive workflow!"  
👉 Tip: Encourage teams to use tools like Kanban boards to visualize their work. Seeing progress keeps everyone on the same page.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
